latestIgtvVideos.title: Zara- The Real Veer
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi, so for the longest time I've wanted to make this video for everyone out there with a pooch
Zara suffered from canine distemper at the age of 6 months(a fatal disease that mostly takes away young pups)
At one point, vets had given up on her and asked us to put her to sleep, it was our lowest, but that's where you need courage and strength to wake up everyday and fight for the one you love.
And this is the story of how she fought, how we fought together
so please, take a few minutes out to watch this and share this, I promise you won't regret it :)
(also sorry for the pathetic voice) lmao
and I really wanna thank everyone who was with her in this journey @zara.not.a.brand
